    dc:description "Figure 3. Holotype female of Anomalon insidiator Smith, 1874 (= Habronyx (H.) insidiator (Smith, 1874)): (a) labels (b) dorsal habitus (c) lateral habitus (d) head, frontal view (e) head, dorsal view (f) head, lateral view (g) mesoscutum, dorsal view (h) scutellum and propodeum, dorsal view (i) mesosoma, lateral view (j) wings." ;
